Dockerfile
fly.toml
README.md

# Build outputs and deps — let the builder produce fresh ones
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.vite

# Persistent data — comes from the mounted volume, not the image
server/data

# Local env / secrets
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Editor / OS noise
.idea
.vscode
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log

# CI / docs that don't belong in the runtime image
.github
